GUI in #RStats exploration revealed book "Programming Graphical User Interfaces in R" (2012). 

3 of the 4 frameworks it covers are now dead!

* {gWidgets} - package is dead/defunct
* {RGtk2} - pkg dead/defunct
* {qtbase} - dead/defunct
* {tcltk} - alive and kicking! https://t.co/0XQI1XZtKV

Please assign percentages to the following: 

The death of GUI framework packages is due to:

1. Rise of Shiny
2. Lack of $$ to maintain complex development
3. Lack of appetite from end-users to learn GUI paradigms (which are aimed at C developers!)

#RStats

While looking into older GUI packages on CRAN, I have "discovered" that the level of instructive documentation for many packages is frickin' woeful!

#RStats https://t.co/1Lvg9xoex9
